Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now enter the populated joint area in about 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Air traffic control satellite 110 inducement beacon reception standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,SOS on the Space Shuttle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Transport ship Orion 108 has entered the control area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The regular ship has come back. Open the communication circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is control satellite 110. Thank you for your effort during the long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nao. Now that I hear your voice, I feel like I have finally arrived at the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a long one this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao, thank you for your effort as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone like us whom you never know when will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you count on machines for sending signals?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that can't be accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a mistake, then there will be a big accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Take care of us next time as well, Nao. -Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-Robita, please take care of inducement. -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't gone to school yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I don't want to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You always say that after a holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, if you don't hurry, you will miss the shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, until when are you going to keep working as an air traffic controller?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why do you care? -Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope you would work on ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is bit lonely, but it's a very important work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't study hard, you won't be able to succeed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to succeed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's what. Tamao's glasses are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibukaki, give them back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything without glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give them back. -It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll give them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where? Where did you put them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha. He's here. He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, are you commuting from a satellite? -Alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Isn't Earth's gravity bit heavy for you? -Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Gosh! -What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Space traffic lights don't need bags, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give it back! -Take it if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are you doing? Give it back! -Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You zero gravity kid, fly here with no gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alien! Space traffic light!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly to the space!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you making fun again? -Atom, don't interrupt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken's father is an air traffic controller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop it, Atom. -But Ken,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going to become a space traffic light anyway when you grow up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you come down to the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Flying, flying. -How is it? Are you watching this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Quick one. It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, it's perfect. Isn't Ken here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, give me my bag back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-All right! -Ken's bag is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back. Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Space traffic light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is an adult doing here? That's expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Naoto! Osamu, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Ken Hoshiyama, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your dad is ill. -Pardon? My dad is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, get aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibukaki, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto and Osamu have all abandoned me and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken's bag. What happened to Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-He blew me and took Ken. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a villain for sure. He blew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mister, the direction is different. -Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, did you fool me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait. Hold on, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was struck hard. I have to repay it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Hey, Atom, try flying faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. Fly slower. I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me to go faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:08:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, that car is headed this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring him? Hurry and get aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You are sure, right? There's only a port for personal rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a sound from this direction for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's that small rocket! -Atom, chase it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Chase it and get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, you must have missed it because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You will figure out the destination if you ask the control center about that rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. That would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,An unexpected small space shuttle is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Small space shuttle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Personal shuttle must have been lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, following the protocol, activate the defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Approaching shuttle, this is a route only for cargo ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to private route.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No change. It's headed right to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear? If you approach more than this, we will fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But after you see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some business there. Can you open the entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you going to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you just have to lead the transport ship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Carolina 3 to a bit different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Carolina 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it contains much pladium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get that much of pladium at once, we will make a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never do such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Robitas here only listen to what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes... I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one is your son. I'm not going to go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hold that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, listen to what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Carolina 3 has entered the control area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You are quick to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead Carolina 3 to the third evacuation point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They told us to wait at the third evacuation point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They told us to take precautions since there is an epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Move to the third evacuation point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we won't need robots anymore. Destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, sir. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What about these ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. We will hold them hostages at a time of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will go to Carolina 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-You keep a close watch. -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Small shuttle is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the quarantine ship. Prepare docking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've caused you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They are pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, something's coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! It doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ken, -Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, two of you, get in the storage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? I'm Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are Ken's classmate... Thank you, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, there's a trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Transport ship with pladium is being attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go save it. Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, take this radio. Let Ken give you directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, please get rid of bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Carolina 3 is at SSW 7 o'clock direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that. Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you will be all right after you do such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off at the place we tell you immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know it's dangerous to not go on the route we are told to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking and move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that sound just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Computer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is broken now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you. Now you won't be safe either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world are these guys' boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was almost over. Atom, you wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom. Atom, there's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,An unattended transport ship is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shuttle from the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's on the settled route, it won't stop if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Carolina 3 is falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dad, Carolina 3 is falling. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom's supporting it, but it's hard. What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-But what should we do? -Be calm, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, look at the right side of the panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Push the DIZ switch on the top right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Change the screen. -This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it look, Ken? Is Carolina 3 within the safe area for re-entering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Dad. It's falling sharply from the green orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Then it will explode with pladium.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh? If that happens... -A great disaster would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do? It will soon melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken! Is Carolina 3's main engine moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then no matter what it takes, raise the ship head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Atom, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Supporting the entire ship is difficult, even if it were for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the ship head point upward. Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-How's it? -No change yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It started to move up, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Change the screen to L3! -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Command Carolina 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the main engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do it, Carolina 3 will be lost in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to stop the main engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But the computer's broken! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it no matter what it takes. Twist open the panel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, Carolina 3 is back in track.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Atom escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! It's done! Now get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch off the main engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring fire extinguisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? We are safe thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just did what Ken told me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the story from Atom. You did a good job. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If Atom weren't there, I wouldn't have been able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And... Are Nao's eyes all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are fine. I am yet to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? You have a great successor next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I can succeed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally have some interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how important what dad does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since today was a crazy day, I don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We have to report it to the police. We also have to repair Robita.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like we'll get busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to school well from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiny in space, Rainbow Comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The 3-3 class astronomy club is going on a field trip by rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened? Rocket's getting dragged to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Crystal! Atlas, you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Atom vs. Atlas IV." Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Atom vs. Atlas IV"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.11,0:23:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:24:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
